    <item>
      <title>拜登的目标是在西部竞选摇摆中保卫内华达州和亚利桑那州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/biden-aims-to-defend-nevada-arizona-in-western-campaign-swing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登正在加紧努力，赢回西部战场州亚利桑那州和内华达州，他的访问旨在巩固2020年支持他但此后逐渐转向的选民的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/biden-aims-to-defend-nevada-arizona-in-western-campaign-swing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
