    <item>
      <title>Gunvor称无人机关闭了俄罗斯60万桶炼油厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/gunvor-says-drones-shut-down-600-000-barrels-of-russia-refining</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Gunvor Group Ltd.首席执行官托比昂·托恩奎斯特(Torbjörn Törnqvist)估计，乌克兰无人机袭击导致俄罗斯每日炼油能力约60万桶被摧毁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/gunvor-says-drones-shut-down-600-000-barrels-of-russia-refining</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:52:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和日本联手警告不要在太空使用核武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/us-and-japan-team-up-to-warn-against-nuclear-weapons-in-space</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和日本提出了一项联合国安理会决议，警告各国不要将核武器送入轨道，因为这加大了对​​俄罗斯的压力，要求其放弃将弹头送入太空的潜在计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/us-and-japan-team-up-to-warn-against-nuclear-weapons-in-space</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:32:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部将在与美国参议员会面时推动 TikTok 的剥离</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/biden-officials-to-brief-wary-senators-on-tiktok-sale-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，司法部和其他机构的高级官员将在周二的闭门简报会上试图说服持怀疑态度的参议员，让他们相信 TikTok 可以继续在美国运营，同时与其中国所有者切断联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/biden-officials-to-brief-wary-senators-on-tiktok-sale-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:31:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储在 6 月降息的可能性不到 50% 的情况下进行价格互换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/fed-swaps-price-in-less-than-50-chance-of-a-june-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于高盛集团的掉期交易员和经济学家预测美联储今年降息幅度较小，两年期国债收益率攀升至今年最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/fed-swaps-price-in-less-than-50-chance-of-a-june-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 16:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院对禁止白宫社交媒体联系人持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/supreme-court-wary-of-ban-on-white-house-social-media-contacts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院表示，它可能会驳回对拜登政府与社交媒体公司接触的限制，审理的案件将影响 2024 年竞选最后几个月解决选举干扰和错误信息问题的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/supreme-court-wary-of-ban-on-white-house-social-media-contacts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 15:43:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克罗地亚总统对法院表示他无法竞选总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/croatia-s-top-court-rules-milanovic-can-t-run-for-premiership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚最高法院表示，总统佐兰·米拉诺维奇突然决定参加下个月的总理选举，这与他的角色“不可调和”，国家元首称这一决定为“政变”，尽管他表示将尊重这一裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/croatia-s-top-court-rules-milanovic-can-t-run-for-premiership</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 13:00:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦维持创纪录利率，国际货币基金组织谈判正在进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/pakistan-keeps-key-rate-at-record-high-with-imf-talks-underway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦央行连续第六次会议将关键利率维持在创纪录的高位，新当选的政府正在与国际货币基金组织进行贷款谈判，希望采取紧缩的货币政策来抑制通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/pakistan-keeps-key-rate-at-record-high-with-imf-talks-underway</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 10:43:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登签署行政命令以促进女性健康研究</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/white-house-unveils-executive-order-to-boost-women-s-health</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统签署了一项行政命令，以加强联邦机构的妇女健康研究标准，并优先考虑其资助，这是缩小长期差距的更广泛努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/white-house-unveils-executive-order-to-boost-women-s-health</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
